criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  sedentarism for at least 6 months;

          -  clinical diagnosis for coronary artery disease (occurrence of any acute coronary
             syndrome, including ST elevation or non-ST elevation myocardial infarction or unstable
             angina or by the diagnosis of obstructive coronary artery disease on coronary
             angiography in patients with stable angina).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  nephropathies;

          -  decompensated cardiovascular diseases;

          -  liver diseases.
